<template lang="pug">
  v-sheet#login(style="height: 100%", color="tblue")
    h1.pt-6.white--text Login
    v-text-field.mt-6.mx-6(solo, placeholder="Email", v-model="email")
    v-text-field.mx-6(solo, placeholder="Contraseña", v-model="password", @keydown.enter="signin")
    .mx-6
      v-btn(color="white", block, light, @click="signin") Iniciar Sesión
</template>

<script lang="pug">
export default Vue.extend({
  data: () => ({
    email: null,
    password: '',
    loading: false,
  }),

  methods: {
    async signin() {
      this.loading = true;
      let result = await this.$store.dispatch('auth/signin', {
        email, password,
      })
      this.loading = false;
      if (result) {
        this.$emit('discard');
      }
    }
  }
})
</script>
